{"tid":1054331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"甩脂機妙用","createTime":"2019-03-09T17:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T18:56:11.000Z","uid":240342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb6822e71061a49d65254e339cedb3515a44086","tid":1054331,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"七年前，我又肥又<del>短</del>矮又毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是呢，就買咗部甩脂機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試咗幾個禮拜之後，發覺根本一啲效都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔想相信自己俾人呃錢，心入面安慰自己：「可能只不過係咁啱對我冇用」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗測試部機，我忍痛送咗畀個肥肥哋嘅外國女性朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇耐之後，佢Youtube channel多咗條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RbmFwMTdUtA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRbmFwMTdUtA&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2GsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=5ef7a671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RbmFwMTdUtA</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爾後，我瘋狂買甩脂機周圍派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7a2c7ec38f85f31ae77b71b313b848164d09c5","tid":1054331,"uid":240342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gxzmj8zWlAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGxzmj8zWlAY&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2GsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=29c7b1a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Gxzmj8zWlAY</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e1734eb2a40ff49d36919ff046d1d7131e2766","tid":1054331,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:26:04.000Z",